    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Supreme executive legislatures, especially the assemblies of citizens having the highest deliberative functions in a government, currently or historically summoned by a monarch for the discussion of important matters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
